{
  "number": 56,
  "name": "سُورَةُ الوَاقِعَةِ",
  "englishName": "Al-Waaqia",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "When the Occurrence occurs,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "There is, at its occurrence, no denial.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "It will bring down [some] and raise up [others].",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "When the earth is shaken with convulsion",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "And the mountains are broken down, crumbling",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "And become dust dispersing.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "And you become [of] three kinds:",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "Then the companions of the right - what are the companions of the right?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "And the companions of the left - what are the companions of the left?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "And the forerunners, the forerunners -",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "Those are the ones brought near [to Allah]",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "In the Gardens of Pleasure,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "A [large] company of the former peoples",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "And a few of the later peoples,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "On thrones woven [with ornament],",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Reclining on them, facing each other.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "There will circulate among them young boys made eternal",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "With vessels, pitchers and a cup [of wine] from a flowing spring -",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "No headache will they have therefrom, nor will they be intoxicated -",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "And fruit of what they select",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "And the meat of fowl, from whatever they desire.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "And [for them are] fair women with large, [beautiful] eyes,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "The likenesses of pearls well-protected,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "As reward for what they used to do.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "They will not hear therein ill speech or commission of sin -",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "Only a saying: \"Peace, peace.\"",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "The companions of the right - what are the companions of the right?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "[They will be] among lote trees with thorns removed",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "And [banana] trees layered [with fruit]",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "And shade extended",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "And water poured out",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "And fruit, abundant [and varied],",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "Neither limited [to season] nor forbidden,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "And [upon] beds raised high.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "Indeed, We have produced the women of Paradise in a [new] creation",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "And made them virgins,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 37,
      "text": "Devoted [to their husbands] and of equal age,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 38,
      "text": "For the companions of the right [who are]",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 39,
      "text": "A company of the former peoples",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 40,
      "text": "And a company of the later peoples.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 41,
      "text": "And the companions of the left - what are the companions of the left?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 42,
      "text": "[They will be] in scorching fire and scalding water",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 43,
      "text": "And a shade of black smoke,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 44,
      "text": "Neither cool nor beneficial.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 45,
      "text": "Indeed they were, before that, indulging in affluence,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 46,
      "text": "And they used to persist in the great violation,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 47,
      "text": "And they used to say, \"When we die and become dust and bones, are we indeed to be resurrected?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 48,
      "text": "And our forefathers [as well]?\"",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 49,
      "text": "Say, [O Muhammad], \"Indeed, the former and the later peoples",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 50,
      "text": "Are to be gathered together for the appointment of a known Day.\"",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 51,
      "text": "Then indeed you, O those astray [who are] deniers,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 52,
      "text": "Will be eating from trees of zaqqum",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 53,
      "text": "And filling with it your bellies",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 54,
      "text": "And drinking on top of it from scalding water",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 55,
      "text": "And will drink as the drinking of thirsty camels.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 56,
      "text": "That is their accommodation on the Day of Recompense.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 57,
      "text": "We have created you, so why do you not believe?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 58,
      "text": "Have you seen that which you emit?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 59,
      "text": "Is it you who creates it, or are We the Creator?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 60,
      "text": "We have decreed death among you, and We are not to be outdone",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 61,
      "text": "In that We will change your likenesses and produce you in that [form] which you do not know.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 62,
      "text": "And you have already known the first creation, so will you not remember?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 63,
      "text": "And have you seen that [seed] which you sow?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 64,
      "text": "Is it you who makes it grow, or are We the grower?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 65,
      "text": "If We willed, We could make it [dry] debris, and you would remain in wonder,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 66,
      "text": "[Saying], \"Indeed, we are [now] in debt;",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 67,
      "text": "Rather, we have been deprived.\"",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 68,
      "text": "And have you seen the water that you drink?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 69,
      "text": "Is it you who brought it down from the clouds, or is it We who bring it down?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 70,
      "text": "If We willed, We could make it bitter, so why are you not grateful?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 71,
      "text": "And have you seen the fire that you ignite?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 72,
      "text": "Is it you who produced its tree, or are We the producer?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 73,
      "text": "We have made it a reminder and provision for the travelers,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 74,
      "text": "So exalt the name of your Lord, the Most Great.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 75,
      "text": "Then I swear by the setting of the stars,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 76,
      "text": "And indeed, it is an oath - if you could know - [most] great.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 77,
      "text": "Indeed, it is a noble Qur'an",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 78,
      "text": "In a Register well-protected;",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 79,
      "text": "None touch it except the purified.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 80,
      "text": "[It is] a revelation from the Lord of the worlds.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 81,
      "text": "Then is it to this statement that you are indifferent",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 82,
      "text": "And make [the thanks for] your provision that you deny [the Provider]?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 83,
      "text": "Then why, when the soul at death reaches the throat",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 84,
      "text": "And you are at that time looking on -",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 85,
      "text": "And Our angels are nearer to him than you, but you do not see -",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 86,
      "text": "Then why do you not, if you are not to be recompensed,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 87,
      "text": "Bring it back, if you should be truthful?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 88,
      "text": "And if the deceased was of those brought near to Allah,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 89,
